sentences.english: Find the subfolder for the version you want to roll back to.
sentences.chinese: 找到您要回滾到的版本對應的子文件夾。

sentences.english: It can also be used to define the default log folder.
sentences.chinese: 還可以使用此屬性來定義缺省日誌文件夾。

sentences.english: The wizard successfully unshared all of the shared folders.
sentences.chinese: 嚮導已成功停止對所有共享文件夾的共享。

sentences.english: A Content Package or Package describes a folder that is used to hold multiple perspectives.
sentences.chinese: 程序包或包是指一個用於保存多個透視圖的文件夾。

sentences.english: Navigate to the product license library or folder where you have your activation keys.
sentences.chinese: 導航到存儲激活密鑰的產品許可證庫或文件夾。

sentences.english: Users can then drag and drop documents into this folder.
sentences.chinese: 用戶然後可以拖放文檔到這個文件夾中。

sentences.english: By default, all packages are transformed to folders.
sentences.chinese: 默認條件下，所有的包都被轉換成了文件夾。

sentences.english: Enter the folder name to store the new e-form.
sentences.chinese: 輸入用於存儲新電子表單的文件夾名稱。

sentences.english: There is an exhaustive list of sample programs provided in the samples folders.
sentences.chinese: 示例文件夾中提供了一個詳盡的示例程序列表。

sentences.english: Please enter a non-blank path for your special folder.
sentences.chinese: 請輸入用來保存該圖像的文件夾路徑。

sentences.english: The folder "%B" cannot be deleted because you do not have permissions to read it.
sentences.chinese: 無法處理文件夾“%B”，因爲您沒有讀取它的權限。

sentences.english: After the file or folder has been updated, double-click to open it for editing.
sentences.chinese: 在更新文件或文件夾後，雙擊可以將其打開進行編輯。

sentences.english: Deleted the new folder during application uninstallation.
sentences.chinese: 在應用程序卸載刪除新的文件夾。

sentences.english: Note that Systems and Databases cannot co-exist in the same customized folder.
sentences.chinese: 注意，系統和數據庫不能在同一自定義文件夾中共存。

sentences.english: You can use this folder to provide your own content.
sentences.chinese: 您可以使用此文件夾提供自己的內容。
